hopobject.name: javascript-tricks
hopobject.body:
I've presented these JavaScript tricks in various venues and I needed to create this project page to collect them a bit so that people can easily check out the source. Most of the demos are actually in the http://github.com/beagleboard/bone101 repository, but that isn't always the easiest to explore. I've make several of them available at live links that make them easy to try out:

jQuery: http://jsfiddle.net/jkridner/3Pe6f/

Flot: http://jsfiddle.net/jkridner/rC4AD/

Processing.JS: http://jsfiddle.net/jkridner/Ag3a9/

Blockly: http://jadonk.github.io/blockly-bonescript/
